#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 6. Sevanāsutta → sevitabbāsevitabbasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an9.6:0.3"
msgid "6. Sevanāsutta "
msgstr "6. Association "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an9.6:1.1"
msgid "Tatra kho āyasmā sāriputto bhikkhū āmantesi … pe … āyasmā sāriputto etadavoca: "
msgstr "There Sāriputta addressed the mendicants: "

