msgid "Cīvarampi, āvuso, duvidhena veditabbaṃ—"
msgstr "You should distinguish two kinds of robes: "

msgctxt "an9.6:2.4"
msgid "sevitabbampi asevitabbampi. "
msgstr "those you should wear, and those you shouldn’t wear. "

msgctxt "an9.6:2.5"
msgid "Piṇḍapātopi, āvuso, duvidhena veditabbo—"
msgstr "You should distinguish two kinds of almsfood: "

msgctxt "an9.6:2.6"
msgid "sevitabbopi asevitabbopi. "
msgstr "that which you should eat, and that which you shouldn’t eat. "

msgctxt "an9.6:2.7"
msgid "Senāsanampi, āvuso, duvidhena veditabbaṃ—"
msgstr "You should distinguish two kinds of lodging: "

